<ab facs="#facs_156_r1l4">dıener cʒu ew geſant hetten von der name wegen / als <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_156_r1l5">der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ~ beẏ <expan cert="unknown">keyerlintech</expan> <expan>geſcheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> iſt / <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_156_r1l7">vnd auch 
<add><ab facs="#facs_156_r1l6">hanſen vörtſchen </ab></add> Eraſms von <expan>Streitp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> / 
<add><ab facs="#facs_156_line_1575571707366_21">vnd </ab></add> <expan>H<ex>er</ex>mans</expan> von Aufſeſʒ / briefe / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_156_r1l9">dıe 
